<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Puttock" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Puttock,</orth> a kite: <cit><quote>who finds the partridge in the --'s nest,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.191" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 191</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a toad, a lizard, an owl, a p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.1.68" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 1, 68</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I chose an eagle, and did avoid a p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.140" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 140</bibl></cit>.
